About the game:

Super Granny returns in Super Granny 5, her latest action-packed adventure! When Dr. Meow zaps Super Granny with a powerful shrink ray, she must journey into the dangerous wilderness of her backyard, battle new granny-eating enemies and rescue her precious kitties from unlikely peril. Help Super Granny collect her missing kitties while running, digging and climbing her way through her own scary backyard. Super Granny 5 features TONS of new content, a hilarious story, puzzle-solving, item-tossing, and 130 addictive levels!
